{"tid":352491,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]有冇人覺得用公帑起嘅所有建築係可以靠民意停用／清拆","createTime":"2017-08-08T21:39:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T03:37:50.000Z","uid":1858,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4fc5bfcad36e17528d481859f5a605e0b4173d76","tid":352491,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T21:39:21.000Z","msg":"根據一個先進民進社會，我覺得既然一個建築係用大家嘅錢去起，大家都應該有權想building繼續運作定停辦，方法好簡單，用類似入稟方法向法庭申請睇下批唔批，過到法律個關之後就全民公投過5成就贏。特別係依家嘅香港，好多野入紙個時講到個成效幾好為左引人上搭，落實左就過橋抽板，起完出黎左兜右兜都達成唔到個誠諾，例子有洗頭鐵同旺角體育城，當然後者賣左地比佢算私人物業吹佢唔脹。咁樣真係好似比人昆完再比人串7多句：死傻閪，錢就比左，野都起埋，你依家吹得我脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，想駁又駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其實我都好清楚呢個提議冇可能發生，大家都係當飛機文睇完算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"f92093df3f23249c9612c9011d3cb3a5bcd7d8b0","tid":352491,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T21:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653369407403202dc406ed03d2679a123b4ff3cf","tid":352491,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T22:16:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7862ce0a624280785cfa65b7ad07baf9cb51d866","tid":352491,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T23:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.g